headline: Vances Ohio Senate Victory Isnt a Big Win for Trump
author: Karl Rove
sentences: Both candidates were ahead of businessman Mike Gibbons at 14%, state Sen. Matt Dolan at a little under 12%, former state GOP Chairwoman Jane Timken at just below 8%, and two others who together held roughly 3%.
The last poll before Mr. Trump endorsed on April 15taken by the Trafalgar Groupshowed Mr. Vance at about 23%, trailing former Treasurer Josh Mandel, who held 28%.
